      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in mint condition. The interior is free of any wear, staining, or damage, with all upholstery, trim, controls, and displays in like-new condition. The exterior has no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. The engine and mechanical systems are in excellent working order with no known issues.",
