    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, functional ride that gets the job done? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, handling your daily commute without drama. It does show its age with some wear and minor imperfections you'd expect from a well-used vehicle, but it's been kept operational and offers solid value for the price. A great option for a budget-conscious buyer who wants reliable transportation without the premium cost!",
      "price": 24500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete, honest picture before you make any decisions. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 expect some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas that reflect the car's age and use. The interior has seen regular use as well, with noticeable wear on the seats, door panels, and dashboard surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though we recommend a pre-purchase inspection as some components may be approaching the end of their service life. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who understands they're getting a well-used vehicle and is comfortable with the associated upkeep. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just an honest car at a fair price.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The interior and exterior show noticeable wear and some cosmetic damage beyond normal use. There are minor mechanical concerns that may require attention. The vehicle is functional but prospective buyers should be prepared for some maintenance costs.",
      "price": 16500.0,
